siriushq/jfiglet
================

	This is a fork of the repository from lalyos/jfiglet <https://github.com/lalyos/jfiglet>.

	It provides a module-info file for JPMS (the original had the commit for this, but it was never released).
	The module name is kept the same, for if an official release is ever published.	

	The latest release is 0.1.0, one increment over their last release (from Apr 15, 2022).

	pom.xml ===================================================
	<repositories>
		<repository>
			<id>jitpack.io</id>
			<url>https://jitpack.io</url>
		</repository>
	</repositories>

	<dependency>
		<groupId>cam.sirius</groupId>
		<artifactId>jfiglet</artifactId>
		<version>0.1.0</version>
	</dependency>
	===========================================================

	module-info.java ==================
	requires com.github.lalyos.jfiglet;
	===================================

what is jfiglet?
================

	This is a Java implementation of FIGfonts to create ASCII art banners, including:
	- `figlet`, small CLI tool for generating banners
	-  `com.github.lalyos.jfiglet.FigletFont`, programmatic usage.

contributing
============

	Contributions are accepted.
	
	Sign off all of your commits with the `Signed-off-by` message footer,
	and submit a PR proposing your change.